'''Mungra''' were a sentient species native to [[Shelsha sector/Legends|Shelsha sector]]. They were furred creatures with orange eyes and large manes who had already established numerous colonies prior to the [[Great Exploration]]. They seemed to use a strict tier system similar to that used by the [[Adarian/Legends|Adarians]]. [[Ydor Vokkoli]] and [[Vicria]] were notable Mungras.

